WEBVTT

00:00:00.090 --> 00:00:25.640
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:27.796 --> 00:01:31.232
=The Maid=

00:01:31.232 --> 00:01:34.048
=Episode 3=

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:36.512
Wait.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:46.960
Are you going back on your word?

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:49.240
I've injured you.

00:01:52.520 --> 00:01:54.120
How can I shirk responsibility?

00:02:05.152 --> 00:02:06.080
Your Highness,

00:02:06.080 --> 00:02:07.120
how should we handle them?

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:09.520
Killing one will warn the rest.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:11.840
If I kill them all,

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:14.880
who would govern the realm
for the Pei family?

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.920
Your mercy is boundless.

00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:22.800
- Thank you for sparing our lives.
- Thank you for sparing our lives.

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.600
Those officials grow
increasingly impertinent.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:36.992
How dare they present

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.360
a courtesan to His Highness?

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:40.360
Given His Highness's exalted status,

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:42.560
those seeking his favor

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:44.040
will naturally employ every means.

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.840
His Highness' heart only belongs to you.

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:47.560
Among so many concubines here,

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.320
none last three months in the mansion.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.600
Pitiful those ladies,

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.680
aspiring to the heavens,

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:57.960
yet fated to fall like paper.

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.360
They lack the fortune

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:02.800
to enjoy the Prince Regent's prosperity.

00:03:26.040 --> 00:03:27.160
I'm fine.

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:29.400
I should go.

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:31.400
Should opportunity arise,

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:33.320
I'll perform for you again.

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.480
You schemed your way into my presence.

00:03:40.440 --> 00:03:43.560
But now, you wish to leave.

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.680
In this world,

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:49.800
what woman doesn't yearn for you?

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.120
But,

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:56.240
one must stay alive
to enjoy such privileges.

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:09.040
You don't strike me as fearing death.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:12.720
In your household,

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.880
there's not even a secondary consort.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.560
Your concubines

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:19.760
either perished tragically

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:21.800
or vanished without trace.

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:25.040
You wish me to stay in the mansion.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.200
But will you protect me?

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.600
With pure intentions,

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.680
you'll naturally survive.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.840
But if harboring ulterior motives,

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:44.160
you'd best remain here briefly.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:47.080
After recovering,

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:50.560
we'll decide your fate.

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:02.800
Such consideration from you

00:05:03.480 --> 00:05:05.000
truly stirs

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:07.360
my heartstrings.

00:05:16.520 --> 00:05:18.920
This must be the dancer
gracing us today.

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:22.160
Your beauty shines true.

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:38.400
You are?

00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:41.920
Lady.

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:43.160
You can speak?

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:48.160
I'm Xiyan. Greetings, Your Highness.

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:51.680
Do you know Xiyan?

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.200
Lady Xiyan

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:58.920
resembles my late sister at home.

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.720
I just miss her.

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:03.040
Your current demeanor

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:05.200
seems less like remembrance,

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:08.680
but more like fear.

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:11.680
Seeing the dead seemingly resurrected,

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:14.480
I neglected decorum.

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:16.320
You must find it amusing.

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:19.800
Forgive me, Your Highness.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:22.160
You've ever been graceful.

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:25.360
Ensure Xiyan receives proper care
these coming days.

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.360
Shen Yuqing,

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.520
cease this pretense.

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:50.200
Your current expression

00:06:50.840 --> 00:06:52.640
makes me wonder

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:57.120
how that sister of yours truly died.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.920
How could it make you tremble so?

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:03.080
Whether you're her

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.240
or not,

00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:07.640
you share her fate,

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:10.360
worthy only to serve as a maid.

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.760
Don't presume ants
can shake mighty trees.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:18.720
Your current demeanor

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:21.200
resembles that bristling Persian cat

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:24.080
from Meixiang House.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.440
You...

00:07:29.640 --> 00:07:31.960
I merely visit briefly,

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:33.720
yet you quake in terror?

00:07:35.720 --> 00:07:37.560
Are you afraid your glory,

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.280
your exclusive favor,

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:41.160
and your power

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:44.000
will all be snatched away by me?

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:51.872
Que'nu,

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:53.920
escort her to the side chamber.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:56.160
Attend her thoroughly.

00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:58.240
Rest assured, Your Highness.

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:01.240
I will extend proper hospitality.

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:05.280
Get in!

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:09.080
In her days at the Duke's Mansion,

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:11.920
Shen Yuqing frequented
Yangque Garden most.

00:08:12.640 --> 00:08:13.880
This side courtyard

00:08:13.880 --> 00:08:16.640
is the closest resemblance
to Yangque Garden here.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.160
Does it feel familiar to you?

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:28.280
If you can't recall,

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:30.000
let me refresh your memory.

00:08:30.920 --> 00:08:31.760
Que'nu,

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:33.560
I am not some delicate young lady

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:35.640
to let a mere maid bully them.

00:08:36.600 --> 00:08:37.480
Today,

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:39.320
I'll show you your place.

00:08:41.056 --> 00:08:41.722
You...

00:08:41.722 --> 00:08:42.920
A household courtesan like you

00:08:42.920 --> 00:08:44.200
dares to humiliate me?

00:08:45.040 --> 00:08:46.560
Let me teach you today

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.680
how to talk to me properly.

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:54.240
Go report this to your master.

00:09:02.016 --> 00:09:03.104
(Don't worry.)

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:06.440
(I'll settle each score one by one.)

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:17.040
The aftermath has been handled.

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:18.760
These deceitful officials

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:20.880
colluded with foreign enemies

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:22.640
to orchestrate your downfall,

00:09:22.760 --> 00:09:24.400
causing massive casualties in our army.

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:27.280
(Cheng Su, Chief Clerk)
The Empress Dowager orchestrated rumors.

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:30.440
Your reputation worsens by the day.

00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:32.520
Empty prestige means nothing.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:35.400
I need only their fear.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.040
You claim no affection for Lady Xiyan,

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:39.600
yet you keep her in the mansion.

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:41.800
Is it because she doesn't fear you?

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:49.880
What makes you think I lack affection?

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:54.000
I'm afraid the whole the capital knows

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:56.280
how deeply I favor her.

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:03.960
If you truly love someone,

00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:07.160
you won't make her a public target.

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:09.360
The women in my mansion

00:10:09.800 --> 00:10:12.040
were all eliminated by Shen Yuanjin.

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:14.880
Using substitutes on the wedding night.

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.360
Borrowing a womb for heirs.

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:20.520
It's time to curb the Princess Consort
and the Duke's Mansion.

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:23.760
Qingmei used to be the top courtesan
in Meixiang House.

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:27.160
I've never heard of Lady Xiyan before.

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.040
Her fragile appearance

00:10:29.280 --> 00:10:30.600
hides cunning ambition.

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:32.040
Your Highness,

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:34.200
don't fall for her honeyed trap.

00:10:39.808 --> 00:10:40.800
Your Highness,

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:42.480
Xiyan can't be Shen Yuqing.

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:45.120
She showed no reaction
to Yangque Garden.

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:47.920
Shen Yuqing couldn't even meet my gaze.

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.200
A mere raised hand

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.360
would make her beg for mercy.

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:52.640
Three years have passed.

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:54.280
People change.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:57.760
We can't confirm through mere words.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:00.040
What if there were a way

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:03.680
to force her true confession...

00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:13.120
Proceed as you suggest.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:20.480
Whether she's Shen Yuqing or not,

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:24.480
I want that face gone from my sight.

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:45.760
(Why this sudden dizziness?)

00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:54.640
Que'nu changed the incense?

00:11:57.400 --> 00:11:58.240
(Qing,)

00:11:58.240 --> 00:11:59.400
(run!)

00:11:59.880 --> 00:12:00.960
(Qing.)

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:03.040
If you and the child escape,

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.800
I'll be free too.

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:06.400
Mother.

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:08.280
Mother.

00:12:08.840 --> 00:12:10.320
Don't touch my mother.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.520
Don't touch my mother.

00:12:11.520 --> 00:12:13.200
I'll fight you to the death!

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:15.680
Don't touch my mother.

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:17.184
Stop.

00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.592
Stop.

00:12:18.592 --> 00:12:19.480
Mother.

00:12:19.480 --> 00:12:22.520
No one could escape my homeland's
heart-devouring incense.

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:25.000
You truly are Shen Yuqing.

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:33.120
Shen Yuqing,

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:34.880
today

00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:36.720
will be your last day.

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.600
Zhao's been in the mountains
for over a month.

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.040
I want to bring him home.

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:50.520
A doting mother ruins the son.

00:12:50.640 --> 00:12:51.680
Henceforth,

00:12:51.680 --> 00:12:53.160
I'll discipline Zhao myself.

00:12:57.720 --> 00:12:59.040
Winter approaches.

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:00.400
Why not move to my quarters?

00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:02.440
Let me attend you nightly,

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:04.360
and ease the morning court duties.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.960
No need for such exertion, my dear.

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.160
The Duke's Mansion needs you,

00:13:16.680 --> 00:13:18.680
as you need it.

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:20.520
We are bound

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:22.520
for life.

00:13:23.160 --> 00:13:24.680
Willful ignorance

00:13:25.640 --> 00:13:26.960
preserves harmony.

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.000
Isn't it better?

00:13:35.680 --> 00:13:36.840
The current state suits me.

00:13:48.440 --> 00:13:49.720
(Music from the side courtyard?)

00:13:50.520 --> 00:13:52.520
(A shameless woman
is always pretentious.)

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:55.040
(So restless even in madness.)

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:06.040
(This music...)

00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:30.160
Tonight you'll either die
by Que'nu's hand,

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:33.480
or meet your end at Pei Ji's blade.

